- Yeah.

47:30.598 --> 47:32.265
Wow. Your dad

47:32.433 --> 47:34.351
seemed like

47:34.519 --> 47:37.354
the fantasy boyfriend.

47:37.522 --> 47:39.105
But he wasn't.

47:41.025 --> 47:43.193
