No, l don't think it's depressing. l-l--

48:10.596 --> 48:12.639
l think--

48:12.807 --> 48:15.892
l think people change and, uh...

48:17.228 --> 48:18.770
and you keep changing

48:18.938 --> 48:22.148
and you make a decision

48:22.316 --> 48:24.568
to change together or...

48:25.570 --> 48:27.696
you split up.

48:32.827 --> 48:34.661
Um...

48:39.584 --> 48:41.751
see you in the morning.

48:41.919 --> 48:43.920
- Good night.
