48:51.012 --> 48:52.762
( sighs )

49:26.464 --> 49:28.048
Hi.

49:30.259 --> 49:32.260
Hey, what are you doing here?

49:33.638 --> 49:35.847
Can l swim with you?

49:37.099 --> 49:40.310
l think you need to have
a grown-up as a lifeguard.

49:43.981 --> 49:46.650
You're a grown-up.

49:46.817 --> 49:49.361
Um, well, that's a good point.

49:49.528 --> 49:52.030
l'm just-- l'm not very--

49:52.198 --> 49:54.949
anyway, let's get you
back to bed, okay?

49:55.117 --> 49:57.160
l won't splash anymore.
l promise.

49:57.328 --> 49:59.788
Can you take me back to my room?

50:00.831 --> 50:03.500
- Um--
- lt's dark.

50:04.627 --> 50:07.712
l-- l don't want to wake
your parents up.

50:07.880 --> 50:10.090
We can walk on tippy-toes.

50:11.175 --> 50:12.509
Okay.

50:30.653 --> 50:33.697
Man.
These stickers--

50:33.864 --> 50:37.158
l had stickers like that
when l was your age,

50:37.326 --> 50:41.663
except l also had
birds and bees and stuff.

50:41.831 --> 50:45.959
