at the Creativity Store.

50:47.712 --> 50:50.004
Well, it's looking good in here.

50:53.759 --> 50:55.260
Mmm.

50:58.806 --> 51:00.390
Okay.

51:02.727 --> 51:04.894
Okay.
Good night.

51:07.481 --> 51:09.899
( synthesizer notes echoing )

51:18.576 --> 51:20.618
So we can listen
to what he's doing on the synth

51:20.786 --> 51:22.829
with the ambient sounds
already in if you want.

51:22.997 --> 51:24.914
Yeah, that would be super helpful.

51:27.585 --> 51:29.627
( note warbling )

51:34.383 --> 51:36.134
lt seems like he wants
to play on the synth

51:36.302 --> 51:38.845
more than actually work on the film.

51:39.013 --> 51:41.264
We'll make it good.
Don't worry.

51:41.432 --> 51:43.266
( notes continuing )

51:44.685 --> 51:46.853
Hey, David, do you want
to run to the store

51:47.021 --> 51:49.731
and pick up that squishy food
for the Foley?

51:49.899 --> 51:52.275
l just want to finish
before the party tonight.

51:52.443 --> 51:54.444
Uh, you don't want to finish this first?

51:54.612 --> 51:57.614
That's okay.
l think Martine can run the board.

51:59.492 --> 52:01.659
Copy that.
Uh, back in 20.

