52:16.175 --> 52:18.134
l don't know how to work the board.

52:18.302 --> 52:20.303
lt'll be fine.
Just hit the space bar,

52:20.471 --> 52:22.263
come back here
and watch it with me.

52:22.431 --> 52:24.766
Okay.

52:24.934 --> 52:26.768
